UNION OPERATION: 
When we have two queries like left query and right query.
union operation combines rows from both the queries.
KEYWORD: UNION

INTERSECT OPERATION:
When we have two queries like left query and right query.
Intersect operation keeps only those rows which are common in both the 
queries.
KEYWORD: INTERSECT


MINUS OPERATION: 
When we have two queries like left query and right query.
Minus operation keeps rows from the left query 
which are not included in the right query.
KEYWORD: EXCEPT
